<p rend="chapter">Byāpetādiyamakagāthā</p>

<p rend="hangnum" n="110"><hi rend="paranum">110</hi><hi rend="dot">.</hi></p>

<p rend="gatha1"> Ekantameva saparatthaparo mahesi,</p>

<p rend="gatha2">Ekantameva dasapāramitābalena;</p>

<p rend="gatha3">Ekantameva hatamārabalena tena,</p>

<p rend="gathalast">Ekantameva suvisuddhamalattha bodhiṃ.</p>
